headline.main: Arsenal Facing Mission Impossible Against Bayern
headline.print_headline: Arsenal Facing Mission Impossible Against Bayern

lead_paragraph: Arsenal will have to produce the biggest second leg comeback in a Champions League knockout tie to avoid a seventh successive exit at the last 16 stage when they host Bayern Munich on Tuesday.
